        <num>CC 713</num>
        <heading>713.  Purchaser with reservation of redemption</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 713.  Purchaser with reservation of redemption.
A purchaser under a reserved right of redemption may establish a predial servitude on the property, but it ceases if the seller exercises his right of redemption.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=110908</p>
